org.forgerock.openam.scripting.sandbox

Class GroovySandboxValueFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kohsuke.groovy.sandbox.GroovyInterceptor
      • org.kohsuke.groovy.sandbox.GroovyValueFilter
        • org.forgerock.openam.scripting.sandbox.GroovySandboxValueFilter

  • public final class GroovySandboxValueFilter
extends org.kohsuke.groovy.sandbox.GroovyValueFilter
    Applies a sandbox to Groovy script execution. Delegates to a Rhino ClassShutter for the actual allow/deny decision for consistency with Rhino Javascript.
